snippet.title: Barrage Populaire - Full Game (both endings) - No Commentary
snippet.description:
"Empêchez les fascistes d'accéder au pouvoir !"

A super cool game about blocking fascists from being elected! And the ending track is amazing!! Loved it! 

[00:03] We lose!
[00:42] We win!

Play it for free: https://docgeraud.itch.io/barrage-populaire
